OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783700376
OL,3,CCourt shown CCTV footage of last time
OL,4,Calleged murder victim seen alive
OL,6,FA court was shown CCTV and mobile
OL,7,Fphone footage of the last time an
OL,8,Falleged murder victim was seen alive
OL,9,Falongside the man accused of his
OL,10,Fmurder in Sticker in Cornwall last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FJames Desborough is accused of
OL,14,Fmurdering Claudio Aquilino, 57,
OL,15,Fsometime between 17 April and 7 July
OL,16,F2025, and Daniel Coleman, 43, sometime
OL,17,Fbetween 2 June and 7 July 2025.
OL,19,FThe prosecution say the footage was
OL,20,Ftaken on the last day of Mr Coleman's
OL,21,Flife on 3 June last year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
