PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783700376
OL,3,CCourt shown CCTV footage of last time
OL,4,Calleged murder victim seen alive
OL,6,FThe first clip shows Desborough and Mr
OL,7,FColeman in Try Dowr JD Wetherspoon in
OL,8,FTruro on June 3, 2025, as they appear
OL,9,Fto walk up to the bar to order drinks.
OL,11,FThe second clip shows Desborough and
OL,12,FMr Coleman at The Falmouth Stable on
OL,13,FJune 3, 2025. In the pub in Falmouth,
OL,14,FDesborough was using Claudio
OL,15,FAquilino's bank card.
OL,17,FThe court was also shown CCTV footage
OL,18,Fof Desborough slap boxing with
OL,19,Fchildren in the street in Truro.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
