PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783700376
OL,3,CCourt shown CCTV footage of last time
OL,4,Calleged murder victim seen alive
OL,6,FA teenager who witnessed the slap
OL,7,Fboxing told the police in an interview
OL,8,Fshown to the court that the exchange
OL,9,Fhad happened after they had spoken to
OL,10,FJames Desborough and the people he was
OL,11,Fwith.
OL,13,FHe said he thought the men were drunk:
OL,14,F"It is not something you would thing
OL,15,Fsomeone would do when they are sober.
OL,16,FI don't know any adults that would do
OL,17,Fslap boxing with children in the
OL,18,Fstreet."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
