OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783700376
OL,3,CCourt shown CCTV footage of last time
OL,4,Calleged murder victim seen alive
OL,6,FThe boy, who cannot be identified for
OL,7,Flegal reasons, said one of the men had
OL,8,Ftold James Desborough to stop when
OL,9,Fthey were boxing. He said videos of
OL,10,Fthe fighting had been circulated.
OL,12,FThe court was previously told that the
OL,13,Ftwo men whose dismembered remains were
OL,14,Ffound in woodland in Sticker in
OL,15,FCornwall met their alleged killer at a
OL,16,Fresidence for homeless people in
OL,17,FNewquay.
OL,19,FThe court heard that the men had been
OL,20,Fliving at the Sandy Lodge Hotel in
OL,21,FNewquay.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
