OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1783700376
OL,3,CCourt shown CCTV footage of last time
OL,4,Calleged murder victim seen alive
OL,6,FA large police search took place in
OL,7,FSticker in July 2025, with specialist
OL,8,Fforensic officers in the woodland for
OL,9,Fseveral days.
OL,11,FJames Desborough denies the murders of
OL,12,FDaniel Coleman and Claudio Aquilino,
OL,13,Fwhose remains were discovered in a
OL,14,Fremote woodland in Sticker in Cornwall
OL,15,Flast year.
OL,17,FHe has previously pleaded guilty to
OL,18,Fpreventing the lawful burial of the
OL,19,Ftwo men's bodies.
OL,21,FThe trial continues.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
